calculateStateEndDate

public static <S extends java.lang.Comparable> java.util.Date calculateStateEndDate(S startState,
                                                                                    S endState,
                                                                                    java.util.List<? extends CertificationStateConfig<S>> configs,
                                                                                    java.util.Date startDate)
Calculate the duration starting at the given start state through the end of the given end state (inclusive). If a start state is not given, start at the first state. If the end state is not given, finish at the last state in the config list.
